claim.claim-text:
1. A motor stator comprising:
an insulating frame having a frame body and a plurality of projecting rods extending from said frame body in the same direction;
an induction unit including an induction circuit board positioned such that said frame body is disposed between said induction circuit board and said projecting rods, a plurality of induction coils embedded within said induction circuit board, and a plurality of coil windings wound respectively around said projecting rods;
a plurality of conductive members extending through and connected to said insulating frame and said induction circuit board, so as to establish an electrical connection between each of said induction coils and a corresponding one of said coil windings.
